#Text=Sunday , May 20 , 2007 .
#Text=Guantánamo detainee David Hicks back in Australia
#Text=Full report : David Hicks transferred from Guantanamo Bay to Australian prison
#Text=A David Hicks supporter .
#Text=Image : Karen Eliot .
#Text=After five years in U.S. military custody , David Hicks has returned to Australia .
#Text=Hicks was taken to the maximum security Yatala Labour Prison , where he will serve the rest of his 9 month sentence .
#Text=His lawyer David McLeod told reporters : " David is well and he enjoyed the trip . ...

#Text=US has paid Pakistan $ 5.6 billion in 5 years for ' war on terror '
#Text=Pervez Musharraf .
#Text=The New York Times reports that the United States are making monthly payments to Pakistan , totalling about $ 1 billion annually , for their efforts against Al-Qaeda and Taliban militants .
#Text=The so-called coalition support funds continued unchanged after President Pervez Musharraf decided to cut back on patrols along the border with Afghanistan .
#Text=" They send us a bill , and we just pay it . ...
